title: Dinosaur National Monument: Partners
body: Explore This Park    Get Involved     Partners            Partners          Intermountain Natural History Association With every book bought in the DinoStore, you can help to support the programs and resources at Dinosaur National Monument. The proceeds from your purchases goes toward helping maintain and improve the exhibits, brochures, and interpretive programs in the monument. These activities are made possible by the Intermountain Natural History Association. Become a member of the Intermountain Natural History Association.
